Package: findomain
Version: 10.0.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, rust, make, cmake
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Findomain/Findomain
Description: The fastest and complete solution for domain recognition
 Findomain is a high‑performance subdomain enumerator that uses
 certificate transparency logs, DNS data, and multiple public APIs.
 It includes subdomain monitoring, alerts via Discord/Slack/Telegram,
 port scanning, HTTP checks, data import from other tools, and full
 support for configuration files.
